<h1><b>HTB Updates</b></h1>
<hr>
<p>HTB Updates is a discord bot that announces your members HackTheBox solves.</p>
<br>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <h3><b>Solve Announcements</b></h3>
        <img class="rounded mw-100" src="/img/solve_announcement.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
